defOutLefVia(25.10)                                        defOutLefVia(25.10)

Name
       defOutLefVia

Syntax
        defOutLefVia {0 | 1}

       Type: Integer

       Default: 0

       Controls  whether  defOut writes out LEF via information in DEF. By de-
       fault, defOut does not write out vias defined in LEF. Set  defOutLefVia
       to 1 to write out LEF vias in the DEF file.

Related Information
              * defOut

              * defOutBySection

